51, 51);\">He also mentioned that the college’s management and staff are en route to Tamale.</p>', 'ep-college-e1693752499846.jpg', '', '', 'Source ', '  5th  September 2023', 1),
(113, '0', 'The Sinister Tale of the Soyjack Torture Mask', '', 'Stories', '<p data-private=\"redact\" class=\"pb-2\" data-wt-guid=\"d90c296d-4271-48d2-8fbf-faf1959a2c43\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\"><wt-ignore uuid=\"9b2855e0-6a1d-4a0f-bfe2-3ed7d26f4e9b\" source=\"wt-feature-result\">In the obscure corners of the internet, a chilling legend has emerged – the Soyjack Torture Mask. This eerie artifact is said to possess a dark power that inflicts torment upon those who dare to wear it. As the story goes, the mask holds a sinister history, shrouded in mystery and horror. In this document, we delve into the chilling origins and the terrifying consequences of the Soyjack Torture Mask.</wt-ignore></p><p data-private=\"redact\" class=\"pb-2\" data-wt-guid=\"572f25c5-f316-4b31-945c-a74e396b5cfa\"><wt-ignore uuid=\"9b2855e0-6a1d-4a0f-bfe2-3ed7d26f4e9b\" source=\"wt-feature-result\">Origins:</wt-ignore></p><p data-private=\"redact\" class=\"pb-2\" data-wt-guid=\"172d57c1-1df4-4baf-9e0b-ee88e73e1eb3\"><wt-ignore uuid=\"9b2855e0-6a1d-4a0f-bfe2-3ed7d26f4e9b\" source=\"wt-feature-result\">Legend has it that the Soyjack Torture Mask was created centuries ago by an enigmatic figure known only as the Maskmaker. Crafted from the bones of tormented souls and imbued with an ancient curse, the mask was intended to be a vessel of suffering. It is said that the Maskmaker\'s malevolent intentions were to punish those who had strayed from the path of masculinity, transforming them into hapless victims of their own fears.</wt-ignore></p><p data-private=\"redact\" class=\"pb-2\" data-wt-guid=\"8bf08e04-3910-4e87-b00b-2f68cc3fa1a5\"><wt-ignore uuid=\"9b2855e0-6a1d-4a0f-bfe2-3ed7d26f4e9b\" source=\"wt-feature-result\">Appearance:</wt-ignore></p><p data-private=\"redact\" class=\"pb-2\" data-wt-guid=\"218f02e0-2747-4c37-9eb4-cbdab49e678d\"><wt-ignore uuid=\"9b2855e0-6a1d-4a0f-bfe2-3ed7d26f4e9b\" source=\"wt-feature-result\">The Soyjack Torture Mask\'s appearance is as unsettling as its reputation. Its design features a grotesque fusion of a soybean and a jack-o\'-lantern, hence its peculiar name. The mask\'s hollow eyes seem to stare into one\'s soul, while its twisted grin hides an unspeakable malevolence. The worn-out, weathered texture suggests a long and haunting history, further adding to its ominous aura.</wt-ignore></p><p data-private=\"redact\" class=\"pb-2\" data-wt-guid=\"2af597ae-219f-4142-8da8-8ca1ce2a01d9\"><wt-ignore uuid=\"9b2855e0-6a1d-4a0f-bfe2-3ed7d26f4e9b\" source=\"wt-feature-result\">The Curse:</wt-ignore></p><p data-private=\"redact\" class=\"pb-2\" data-wt-guid=\"59e5a5a0-3cf4-4c60-bb05-ea9ededfb3f7\"><wt-ignore uuid=\"9b2855e0-6a1d-4a0f-bfe2-3ed7d26f4e9b\" source=\"wt-feature-result\">Once donned, the Soyjack Torture Mask is said to consume its wearer\'s identity, plunging them into a nightmarish realm of psychological torment. Victims report experiencing vivid hallucinations, their deepest fears coming to life with horrifying clarity. The mask feeds off their distress, amplifying it to unbearable levels.</wt-ignore></p><p data-private=\"redact\" class=\"pb-2\" data-wt-guid=\"f5a675c8-a202-4ef8-be9c-fc99d86dabaa\"><wt-ignore uuid=\"9b2855e0-6a1d-4a0f-bfe2-3ed7d26f4e9b\" source=\"wt-feature-result\">Consequences:</wt-ignore></p><p data-private=\"redact\" class=\"pb-2\" data-wt-guid=\"dc1219f5-75af-4b80-b1ae-3a66508566ba\"><wt-ignore uuid=\"9b2855e0-6a1d-4a0f-bfe2-3ed7d26f4e9b\" source=\"wt-feature-result\">As the curse takes hold, the unfortunate wearer becomes trapped in a never-ending cycle of anguish. Sleep becomes elusive, as nightmares blend with reality, blurring the boundaries between the two. The once-confident souls who donned the mask are reduced to trembling wrecks, haunted by their deepest insecurities.</wt-ignore></p><p data-private=\"redact\" class=\"pb-2\" data-wt-guid=\"9c5c31e8-b882-441b-9ddf-e25790deba2d\"><wt-ignore uuid=\"9b2855e0-6a1d-4a0f-bfe2-3ed7d26f4e9b\" source=\"wt-feature-result\">Legend and Lore:</wt-ignore