(125, '0', 'Does this image deserve 10,000 shares?', '', 'lifestyle', '<p data-private=\"redact\" class=\"pb-2\" data-wt-guid=\"4261990c-0d87-443c-9715-0d0167c5f7a5\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\">Does this image deserve 10,000 shares? <wt-ignore uuid=\"ccf82566-51e7-44e0-867f-2756b410aa6f\" source=\"wt-feature-result\">This</wt-ignore> image displays a funny chat between two ex lovers. <wt-ignore uuid=\"bdf97bbf-d517-4d20-bce9-2d4ce1459a83\" source=\"wt-feature-result\">Probably not, but it\'s worth a good laugh!</wt-ignore> This type of content can be an emotional trigger for many <wt-ignore uuid=\"b19c5ea5-e211-4319-959a-466861b865e9\" source=\"wt-feature-result\">people. In</wt-ignore> their chat, <wt-ignore uuid=\"e99862b9-a377-4460-aa69-1922a7292399\" source=\"wt-feature-result\">Fatima</wt-ignore> informed <wt-ignore uuid=\"0b510797-14cc-479b-a1ae-a947c95a47e7\" source=\"wt-feature-result\">Ahmad</wt-ignore> about her getting a car <wt-ignore uuid=\"4b8c80c6-4d82-4cbb-a027-e93aa1742241\" source=\"wt-feature-result\">licence.</wt-ignore></p><p data-private=\"redact\" class=\"pb-2\" data-wt-guid=\"b7ce82b0-5be4-4de4-9172-8b194c7b10a9\">Ahmad on the other hand sees no reason for such information, but according to <wt-ignore uuid=\"94be7ea4-d6a5-491e-81f2-f53c5c97eb93\" source=\"wt-feature-result\">Fatima, Ahmad</wt-ignore> should look carefully before crossing the road because he can knock him down anytime.</p>', 'main-qimg-ef521161a1948fa43e776c458d56a1cf.jpg', '', '', 'source ', '  10th  September 2023', 1);
