(150, '0', 'Black Sherif blasts fan for alleging that he is sold his soul ', 'Black-Sherif-blasts-fan-for-alleging-that-he-is-sold-his-soul-', 'entertainmen', '<p data-private=\"redact\" class=\"pb-2\" data-wt-guid=\"e499b578-24b6-4c24-b4fe-53a3325be577\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\"><wt-ignore uuid=\"f1f0d392-6263-4d60-8a9f-1c5cc1e80316\" source=\"wt-feature-result\">Jokingly, he replied that the fan might have already sold his soul if he knew where to do so.</wt-ignore></p><p data-private=\"redact\" class=\"pb-2\" data-wt-guid=\"a8294b08-3678-4f8a-99a7-958827f852cf\"><wt-ignore uuid=\"d14762c1-5b0d-40c2-99ba-ce3c6c62b332\" source=\"wt-feature-result\">\"You sell souls, Jon, but who wants to sell your soul more than me? Do you even know where they sell souls?\" he asked.</wt-ignore></p><p data-private=\"redact\" class=\"pb-2\" data-wt-guid=\"58cd81cd-8aab-4f47-880b-afdc9809b402\"><wt-ignore uuid=\"84b32db2-23f1-41e8-b33a-f7f3ba672438\" source=\"wt-feature-result\">Mohammed Ismail Sherif, better known as Black Sherif, is making waves in the music industry.</wt-ignore></p><p data-private=\"redact\" class=\"pb-2\" data-wt-guid=\"ec53525e-3b19-4e57-ae86-715e7fe59184\"><wt-ignore uuid=\"f4857879-bd2e-4dfc-a1db-2c213a477d56\" source=\"wt-feature-result\">As the reigning VGMA Artiste of the Year performed his hit songs and songs from his widely-shared album at Palladium Times Square, hordes of enthusiastic fans gathered to witness his debut.</wt-ignore></p><p data-private=\"redact\" class=\"pb-2\" data-wt-guid=\"1899d524-f9e4-4fb3-8001-cf6d1497b040\"><wt-ignore uuid=\"25b4e5fc-c497-4493-9fa2-e0f560b67b82\" source=\"wt-feature-result\">Some fans noticed strange imagery on the stage backdrop, raising questions despite the excitement and fan frenzy surrounding the event.</wt-ignore> <wt-ignore uuid=\"9cec0413-67f1-48a3-9f3c-47cb0ff52c5c\" source=\"wt-feature-result\">There was a figure with horns and eerie red eyes on the set.</wt-ignore></p><p data-private=\"redact\" class=\"pb