(151, '0', ' 27 YEAR OLD WELDER FROM KROBO  UNVEILED A PROTOTYPE OF HIS VEHICLE ', '-27-YEAR-OLD-WELDER-FROM-KROBO-UNVEILED-A-PROTOTYPE-OF-HIS-VEHICLE-', 'mechanical', '<p>Sylvester Kweku, the 27 year old welder from Otrokper in the Upper Manya Krobo District in the Eastern Region who dropped out of basic school to pursue his cherished dream in welding.</p><p><br></p><p>He underwent apprenticeship for 3 years at Agormanor in the Lower Manya Krobo Municipality and subsequently honed his skill at Labadi, Accra for 2 years.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p>He has been into this beautiful craftsmanship, and has actively been producing varied machines and gadgets for the past including including fufu grinding machine, corn millers, cassava grinding machines.</p><p><br></p><p>The new vehicle is just an addition to his works. He\'s already molded a helicopter, tested it at the Koforidua Sports st…</p>', 'WhatsApp Image 2023-09-18 at 16.54.32.jpeg', '', '', 'Source ', '  18th  September 2023', 1),
