(165, '0', 'What is clogged toilet ?  here is How to prevent a clogged toilet', 'What-is-clogged-toilet-here-is-How-to-prevent-a-clogged-toilet', 'plumbing', '<p data-private=\"redact\" class=\"pb-2\" data-wt-guid=\"8edac587-dfca-489d-9ba5-16e2a566dace\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\"><wt-ignore uuid=\"c34aeef3-5397-4d66-aff1-7ad8c9ed33d7\" source=\"wt-feature-result\">Clogged toilets are a common household problem that can cause inconvenience and frustration. A clogged toilet occurs when the waste and water cannot flow freely through the plumbing system. This blockage can be caused by a variety of factors, including excessive toilet paper, foreign objects, or a buildup of waste materials.</wt-ignore></p><p data-private=\"redact\" class=\"pb-2\" data-wt-guid=\"e08da747-f7a9-4f42-849a-38f8044c1b22\"><wt-ignore uuid=\"c34aeef3-5397-4d66-aff1-7ad8c9ed33d7\" source=\"wt-feature-result\">To prevent a clogged toilet, there are several simple steps you can take. First, be mindful of the amount of toilet paper you use. Excessive use of toilet paper can easily lead to a clog. Use only as much as necessary, and consider using thinner or less absorbent toilet paper if clogs are a recurring issue.</wt-ignore></p><p data-private=\"redact\" class=\"pb-2\" data-wt-guid=\"d8460c9c-7586-49cf-9d04-76c4814c7faa\"><wt-ignore uuid=\"c34aeef3-5397-4d66-aff1-7ad8c9ed33d7\" source=\"wt-feature-result\">In addition to being mindful of toilet paper usage, it\'s important to avoid flushing any foreign objects down the toilet. Items such as paper towels, feminine hygiene products, or baby wipes should never be flushed, as they do not break down easily and can cause blockages in the plumbing system.</wt-ignore></p><p data-private=\"redact\" class=\"pb-2\" data-wt-guid=\"941c68d4-46d0-4efa-bf91-06d3506b7ed6\"><wt-ignore uuid=\"c34aeef3-5397-4d66-aff1-7ad8c9ed33d7\" source=\"wt-feature-result\">Regular maintenance is also crucial in preventing clogged toilets. Consider using a plunger to clear any minor blockages before they worsen. Additionally, using a toilet auger or snake can help to remove any stubborn clogs that may be deeper in the plumbing system.</wt-ignore></p><p data-private=\"redact\" class=\"pb-2\" data-wt-guid=\"39d7ceb0-e3f7-41d6-9c84-9b6b1afcf4c2\"><wt-ignore uuid=\"c34aeef3-5397-4d66-aff1-7ad8c9ed33d7\" source=\"wt-feature-result\">Furthermore, it\'s important to educate children about proper toilet usage. Ensure that they understand what should and should not be flushed down the toilet. Installing a childproof toilet lock can also prevent young children from accidentally causing a clog.</wt-ignore></p><p data-private=\"redact\" class=\"pb-2\" data-wt-guid=\"dd978a5c-7e13-4269-b380-d78962abe525\"><wt-ignore uuid=\"c34aeef3-5397-4d66-aff1-7ad8c9ed33d7\" source=\"wt-feature-result\">In conclusion, a clogged toilet is a common plumbing issue that can disrupt daily life. By following these preventive measures, such as being mindful of toilet paper usage, avoiding flushing foreign objects, regularly maintaining the toilet, and educating children about proper toilet usage, you can minimize the occurrence of clogs and ensure a properly functioning toilet.</wt-ignore></p>', 'iStock-1457073079.jpg', '', '', 'source ', '  23rd  September 2023', 1),
