(186, '0', 'Here are ten truths everyone should accept in life', 'Here-are-ten-truths-everyone-should-accept-in-life', 'lifestyle', '<ol class=\"list-decimal px-8\" data-wt-guid=\"3f370a7e-d27c-4244-a537-c6c7e68a251f\" data-pm-slice=\"3 3 []\"><li><p data-private=\"redact\" class=\"pb-2\" data-wt-guid=\"e6acf36a-c2e9-4e68-870a-b6746646090f\"><strong>You </strong><span class=\"issue-underline underline decoration-2 underline-offset-4 transition decoration-border-brand-default [.long-form-editing-active_&amp;]:decoration-border-brand-default/50 hover:bg-bg-brand-light-default\" data-issueid=\"6cad1b06-4166-4850-a715-2c84fcc11cd2\" aria-label=\"open issue for the following text are not going to exist\" data-testid=\"issue-underline:undefined\"><strong>are not going to exist</strong></span><strong> forever. You’re just a tiny speck in this vast universe and your time in this world is limited</strong>. <wt-ignore uuid=\"829b15f8-6b26-4096-a74f-a2859e4ad84a\" source=\"wt-feature-result\">Appreciate life, live in the present, and make the most of every moment. Love and be loved. Forgive and be forgiven.</wt-ignore></p></li><li><p data-private=\"redact\" class=\"pb-2\" data-wt-guid=\"6d6bc868-6397-414a-b973-6b8a69bb7d19\"><strong>Anything harsh said to a loved one in anger leaves a permanent scar, no matter how much you try to bandage:</strong>  It\'s important to remember that your words have the power to hurt and to heal. Take the time to think before you speak and be mindful of the way you approach others. Choose to be kind and forgiving, and remember that life is too short to be spent with regrets. </p></li><li><p data-private=\"redact\" class=\"pb-2\" data-wt-guid=\"5275c7e1-e8bf-40b7-99bc-e6bae2262758\">Health is the most important wealth you can <wt-ignore uuid=\"2ffb8074-b23f-4c84-8813-6144a514630f\" source=\"wt-feature-result\">acquire. No</wt-ignore> matter how much gold you own, it <wt-ignore uuid=\"5fcc9c67-8c1d-41cc-885e-98b6c56c58ac\" source=\"wt-feature-resul