(193, '0', 'Hearts of Oak banned by FIFA', 'Hearts-of-Oak-banned-by-FIFA', 'sports', '<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: start;\">FIFA has stepped in decisively regarding the ongoing dispute involving Hearts of Oak, imposing a transfer ban on the club due to their failure to settle an outstanding debt of $14,002 owed to former coach Slavko Matic.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: start;\">The international football governing body has also called upon the Ghana Football Association to enforce this ban at the national level, intensifying the repercussions for Hearts of Oak.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: start;\">The root of this controversy traces back to March 2023 when Serbian coach Slavko Matic was abruptly relieved of his duties. His dismissal occurred amidst a tumultuous backdrop, with enraged supporters confronting him during a training session.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: start;\">Following these events, Matic lodged a formal complaint with the Ghana Police, expressing concerns for his personal safety. In response, Hearts of Oak conveyed their inability to ensure the coach’s security.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: start;\">In light of these developments, Matic escalated the matter to FIFA, resulting in a verdict issued in July of the same year. FIFA ruled in favor of Matic, ordering Hearts of Oak to compensate their former coach with the sum of $14,002 for the breach of his contract.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: start;\">Regrettably, Hearts of Oak has not adhered to FIFA’s directive, prompting the international body to impose the transfer ban as a punitive measure. This embargo, which is already in effect, restricts the club from registering new players until they fulfill their financial obligations&nbsp;to&nbsp;Matic</p>', 'accra-hearts-of-oak.jpg', '', '', 'Source ', '  25th  September 2023', 1);
