ned\">get jealous of</span> each other.</p><p data-private=\"redact\" class=\"pb-2\" data-wt-guid=\"c72f99af-2421-4fed-8104-b8a101f18216\">12. Invest in <span class=\"issue-underline underline decoration-2 underline-offset-4 transition decoration-border-brand-default [.long-form-editing-active_&amp;]:decoration-border-brand-default/50 hover:bg-bg-brand-light-default\" data-issueid=\"7085297b-e056-47a6-ab3e-65c51a93a8ea\" aria-label=\"open issue for the following text a good\" data-testid=\"issue-underline:undefined\">a good</span> <span class=\"issue-underline underline decoration-2 underline-offset-4 transition decoration-border-brand-default [.long-form-editing-active_&amp;]:decoration-border-brand-default/50 hover:bg-bg-brand-light-default\" data-issueid=\"936b5b8d-e423-46ed-9c73-29a8ec09e2f0\" aria-label=\"open issue for the following text wardrobe, a good niche\" data-testid=\"issue-underline:undefined\">wardrobe, a good niche</span> fragrance, and learn how to talk. You\'ll boost your success rate by 94%.</p><p data-private=\"redact\" class=\"pb-2\" data-wt-guid=\"e9550fc3-0a72-4c97-b93d-e97d214db54e\">13. Befriend nature, walk 10,000 steps per day to clear your mind, boost your mood and get creative.</p><p data-private=\"redact\" class=\"pb-2\" data-wt-guid=\"e16f59ef-4348-4ba6-a450-4f3c5876ec95\">14. <wt-ignore uuid=\"f1400467-61cf-4639-9e3c-3c58d511f86c\" source=\"wt-feature-result\">Keep a distance</wt-ignore> from people who only prioritize their needs over yours. They\'re your greatest setback.</p><p data-private=\"redact\" class=\"pb-2\" data-wt-guid=\"cc8f7ed2-fa8f-4267-bbcf-b48798a0cf89\">15. Be smart enough to quit weed, porn, and alcohol. They\'re the worst <wt-ignore uuid=\"3900ada8-bf3e-4620-8c78-0083d64bd61e\" source=\"wt-feature-result\">distractions</wt-ignore> that\'ll raise your dopamine, make you dumb, and <wt-ignore uuid=\"5299056b-494c-4746-be00-a60881e09064\" source=\"wt-feature-result\">depress.</wt-ignore></p>', 'iStock-1447673007.jpg',